            <thetext>Main changes for supporting Android 4.0:

- Support a software-based Navigation Bar. Android 4.0 removes the need for traditional hardware keys.
- Maybe the new feature &quot;action bar&quot; should be adapted.
- Design adaption for tab bar (&quot;Fixed Tabs&quot;), buttons, lists, text field, switches (See: http://developer.android.com/design/building-blocks/tabs.html)
   These adaptions are only design fixes, like other button colors or borders.
- Some adaptions are not trivial to realize/adapt: Spinners, Seek Bars or Pickers. Spinners and Pickers are not realized in qooxdoo mobile yet.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
